nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE MAINTAINS ITS STRENGTH WELL TO THE EAST OF HAWAII...
summary: ...HENRIETTE MAINTAINS ITS STRENGTH WELL TO THE EAST OF HAWAII... As of 11:00 PM HST Wed Aug 06 the center of Henriette was located near 18.4, -133.9 with movement W at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
